WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:52.120 --> 01:54.400
A bracelet with my initials on it.

01:56.960 --> 01:57.960
What does that mean?

02:09.280 --> 02:11.920
What does a bracelet mean as a gift?

02:16.520 --> 02:18.040
"BRACELET" SOUNDS LIKE
"CHERISHED LOVE"

02:18.120 --> 02:19.200
IT'S A GIFT FOR LOVERS

02:19.280 --> 02:20.320
Love?

02:26.160 --> 02:28.920
BEFORE GIVING THE BRACELET,
LEARN OF THE RECIPIENT'S PREFERENCES

02:29.000 --> 02:30.080
"From an elder,

02:30.720 --> 02:32.600
it means forever caring."

02:35.080 --> 02:36.880
Okay, I get it.

02:46.400 --> 02:47.360
Here.

02:53.440 --> 02:55.000
You're home.

02:55.080 --> 02:56.760
Have you packed your things?

02:56.840 --> 02:57.920
I haven't started packing.

02:58.960 --> 03:00.280
Are you still not done packing?

03:00.840 --> 03:02.080
I'll do it later.

03:02.160 --> 03:04.440
Were you waiting for me
to come home to pack for you?

03:04.520 --> 03:05.400
No.

03:05.960 --> 03:07.720
By the way, Mom and Dad.

03:07.800 --> 03:10.640
Jiaxu will pick me up tomorrow morning

03:10.720 --> 03:11.880
to go to the airport together.

03:11.960 --> 03:13.760
We're on the same flight,

03:13.840 --> 03:15.440
so we'll return to Yihe together.

03:15.520 --> 03:16.480
What a coincidence.

03:17.120 --> 03:19.400
Now you can sleep in tomorrow morning.

03:20.000 --> 03:21.840
Okay, that works out.

03:21.920 --> 03:24.360
- Then…
- Our car is on restricted use tomorrow.

03:24.440 --> 03:25.400
Yes, that's true.

03:25.480 --> 03:27.160
Well, remember to call regularly

03:27.240 --> 03:28.560
when you get back.

03:28.640 --> 03:30.800
No, video call us when you arrive.

03:30.880 --> 03:32.200
I know.

03:32.280 --> 03:33.360
Video call, okay?

03:34.960 --> 03:35.840
Good night.

03:35.920 --> 03:37.080
Good night. Good girl.

03:37.160 --> 03:38.520
- Good night.
- I'll miss you.

03:39.040 --> 03:39.960
- Go and rest.
- Okay.

03:40.040 --> 03:41.720
- I'm sleepy.
- Okay. Your dad drank a lot.

03:41.800 --> 03:43.040
- Bye.
- Okay, bye.

03:43.120 --> 03:43.960
Sleep early, okay?

03:44.040 --> 03:45.000
Bye.

04:01.240 --> 04:02.720
NANWU TO YIHE, 9:50 TO 12:45

04:02.800 --> 04:04.080
TICKET SUCCESSFULLY CANCELED

04:04.160 --> 04:05.040
CONFIRM

04:14.680 --> 04:17.000
NANWU TO YIHE, 08:20 TO 10:10

04:19.959 --> 04:21.360
CONFIRM PAYMENT

04:21.440 --> 04:23.320
PAYMENT FAILED

04:26.040 --> 04:28.000
NANWU TO YIHE,
NO MATCHING RESULTS FOUND

04:28.880 --> 04:31.120
NANWU TO YIHE,
NO MATCHING RESULTS FOUND

04:34.360 --> 04:41.000
PURCHASE PLANE TICKETS

04:41.960 --> 04:44.360
PROGRAMMERS OF THE DREAM GAMES

04:44.440 --> 04:45.680
Guys, sorry to disturb you.

04:45.760 --> 04:47.560
I have an important meeting

04:47.640 --> 04:48.800
to attend in Yihe tomorrow.

04:49.320 --> 04:51.520
I must take this flight back.

04:51.600 --> 04:52.640
Can you guys

04:53.320 --> 04:55.800
please click on this link
to help me get a ticket?

04:55.880 --> 04:56.760
Thank you.

05:13.800 --> 05:15.520
SHARE WITH FRIENDS
TO BOOK FASTER AS A VIP

05:21.120 --> 05:23.520
NANWU TO YIHE, 8:20 TO 11:15

05:55.680 --> 05:56.600
Good morning.

05:58.240 --> 05:59.080
Good morning.

06:12.840 --> 06:15.680
Jiaxu, did you not sleep well last night?

06:18.120 --> 06:20.600
I had some work to deal with yesterday.

06:21.560 --> 06:22.400
Your breakfast.

06:24.080 --> 06:25.040
Thank you.

06:35.120 --> 06:36.360
Where's the thing I gave you?

06:40.960 --> 06:41.880
Do you not like it?

06:48.440 --> 06:49.600
Let's go.

07:20.120 --> 07:21.760
Jiaxu, did you not have breakfast?

07:22.840 --> 07:23.760
No.

07:30.560 --> 07:31.640
Have this then.

07:34.240 --> 07:35.080
Thank you.

07:41.120 --> 07:42.600
Will juice alone fill you up?

07:45.920 --> 07:46.800
Yes.

07:47.640 --> 07:48.840
Open your mouth.

07:57.760 --> 07:58.800
Take this and eat it.

08:01.000 --> 08:01.840
Wait.

08:18.760 --> 08:19.600
Thank you.

08:38.080 --> 08:39.480
We still have time before boarding.

08:40.600 --> 08:42.039
Let's sit here and rest for a while.

08:52.080 --> 08:52.920
Here.

08:55.240 --> 08:56.280
Duan Jiaxu?

08:58.520 --> 09:00.440
It's Yuan Lang. From high school!

09:00.520 --> 09:01.800
- Yuan Lang.
- Yes!

09:01.880 --> 09:03.480
- It has been a while.
- Yes, it has been.

09:03.560 --> 09:04.840
Sit down.

09:04.920 --> 09:06.280
How many years has it been now?

09:07.360 --> 09:08.840
We had a class reunion recently.

09:08.920 --> 09:09.880
Why didn't you come?

09:11.520 --> 09:13.960
I was too busy with work at that time,

09:14.040 --> 09:15.080
so I couldn't go.

09:16.160 --> 09:17.240
I heard from Jiang Ying

09:17.320 --> 09:19.720
that you're excelling at work
and very busy.

09:19.800 --> 09:21.280
You're earning quite a bit, right?

09:22.160 --> 09:23.440
It's okay.

09:24.600 --> 09:26.360
Is this your girlfriend?

09:31.280 --> 09:32.120
No, my mistake.

09:32.200 --> 09:33.480
I heard

09:33.560 --> 09:35.080
that you and Jiang Ying are together.

09:36.120 --> 09:37.840
Jiang Ying and I?

09:39.360 --> 09:40.440
Who told you that?

09:41.440 --> 09:42.320
Are you not?

09:44.280 --> 09:46.280
I don't remember who told me.

09:47.440 --> 09:48.400
I was mistaken.

09:49.840 --> 09:51.040
Sorry about that.

09:51.120 --> 09:52.360
I speak without thinking.

09:53.480 --> 09:54.600
I was just spouting nonsense.

09:56.560 --> 09:57.880
It's time for me to board.

09:57.960 --> 09:58.960
I'll get going first.

09:59.040 --> 10:01.080
See you. Come to the next reunion, okay?

10:01.160 --> 10:02.000
See you.

10:14.280 --> 10:15.240
So…

10:18.520 --> 10:19.760
Who is Jiang Ying?

10:24.040 --> 10:26.080
It's the woman we ran into during dinner

10:26.160 --> 10:27.320
on New Year's Eve.

10:31.960 --> 10:33.720
It's not that kind of relationship.

10:36.600 --> 10:38.240
You also saw how she treated me.

10:38.800 --> 10:40.520
How could I have anything to do with her?

10:49.320 --> 10:50.200
Besides,

10:51.320 --> 10:52.920
didn't I promise you before?

10:53.880 --> 10:55.280
If I get a girlfriend,

10:55.840 --> 10:57.080
I'll introduce her to you first.

11:09.800 --> 11:12.960
But I remember
there was another woman before.

11:14.560 --> 11:15.880
I came to Yihe

11:15.960 --> 11:17.840
when I was in high school.

11:18.840 --> 11:20.560
You came to the airport

11:21.680 --> 11:22.680
with her.

11:25.960 --> 11:28.240
Did you think she was my girlfriend?

11:33.960 --> 11:34.840
No.

11:36.280 --> 11:37.960
I'm just

11:40.120 --> 11:41.000
asking.

11:46.880 --> 11:52.200
BOARDING PASS

11:55.880 --> 11:56.800
So

11:58.040 --> 12:00.920
he never forgot
what he promised me back then.

12:02.680 --> 12:04.040
He didn't lie to me.

12:05.640 --> 12:06.880
I misunderstood him back then.

12:28.040 --> 12:30.520
CHAPTER 14, CONNECTION

12:30.600 --> 12:32.320
THE MOST BEAUTIFUL ANTICIPATION

13:04.160 --> 13:05.280
Bye.

13:11.520 --> 13:12.840
When did you arrive?

13:12.920 --> 13:14.920
Just ten minutes earlier than you.

13:15.000 --> 13:16.400
So what are you doing?

13:21.440 --> 13:22.560
Did he see you back here?

13:24.960 --> 13:27.400
So which identity did he use
to see you back?

13:31.120 --> 13:32.360
I'm not sure.

13:34.360 --> 13:36.560
You're not sure? Why do you say that?

13:36.640 --> 13:37.600
Did something happen?

13:40.240 --> 13:41.720
He told me

13:42.400 --> 13:45.280
he hasn't dated for the past few years.

13:46.360 --> 13:47.880
Did he volunteer that information?

13:50.560 --> 13:51.960
I guess so.

13:53.560 --> 13:55.320
Then what else are you unsure about?

14:00.520 --> 14:01.560
Weiwei,

14:01.640 --> 14:03.440
do you remember what I told you before?

14:04.160 --> 14:07.560
His way of speaking and personality

14:08.560 --> 14:09.520
is sort of…

14:11.880 --> 14:13.080
But I do think

14:13.840 --> 14:15.640
that he has been a bit strange lately.

14:15.720 --> 14:16.840
Strange?

14:16.920 --> 14:19.480
He's even stranger than before.

14:19.560 --> 14:20.680
I just feel that…

14:21.400 --> 14:23.160
He makes me feel

14:23.240 --> 14:24.600
that he might have feelings…

14:25.960 --> 14:28.360
I might be overthinking it

14:28.440 --> 14:29.720
or I am being too sensitive.

14:31.160 --> 14:32.200
Do you think

14:33.080 --> 14:34.960
- that he also likes you?
- No.

14:38.560 --> 14:39.600
Well, not really.

14:40.440 --> 14:41.560
Then what is it?

14:44.000 --> 14:45.760
Maybe just a tiny bit.

14:47.360 --> 14:49.680
Gosh, you're such a coward.

14:49.760 --> 14:51.800
How can you be afraid to even say it?

14:52.360 --> 14:53.520
What is so bad about you?

14:54.400 --> 14:55.960
I just think

14:56.960 --> 14:58.200
that it's impossible between us.

15:00.000 --> 15:01.560
I've always had this feeling

15:02.400 --> 15:04.160
precisely because I like him.

15:04.960 --> 15:07.760
So even when he does something normal,

15:07.840 --> 15:09.320
I misinterpreted his intentions.

15:10.680 --> 15:11.560
Sangsang.

15:11.640 --> 15:13.360
It's not a recent development.

15:13.440 --> 15:14.960
I'm familiar with this feeling.

15:19.520 --> 15:22.360
Considering our relationship,

15:23.840 --> 15:25.560
a change wouldn't be easy.

15:33.320 --> 15:35.320
Sangsang, tell me.

15:35.400 --> 15:37.280
What exactly are you worried about?

15:42.240 --> 15:43.520
If he were a stranger

15:46.040 --> 15:48.360
or someone who hadn't watched me grow up,

15:49.920 --> 15:51.160
I would definitely pursue him

15:51.960 --> 15:53.160
if I liked him this much.

15:54.560 --> 15:56.080
Even if it means being ghosted

15:56.720 --> 15:57.640
or being rejected,

15:57.720 --> 15:59.000
I wouldn't be afraid.

15:59.920 --> 16:02.560
But because this person
watched me grow up,

16:03.160 --> 16:05.160
could he really have such feelings for me?

16:05.720 --> 16:08.440
How is he someone who watched you grow up?

16:08.520 --> 16:09.960
At most,

16:10.520 --> 16:12.760
he's a big brother that you met
when you were a child.

16:14.840 --> 16:15.920
I'll tell you what I think.

16:16.000 --> 16:17.440
So you listen, okay?

16:17.520 --> 16:20.080
I'm looking at this
from an observer's perspective.

16:20.160 --> 16:21.280
Now, both of you

16:21.920 --> 16:23.080
are adults, right?

16:23.760 --> 16:25.720
Even if he is
four or five years older than you,

16:26.320 --> 16:28.000
so what?

16:28.080 --> 16:29.200
In today's society,

16:29.280 --> 16:32.200
even an eight-year gap isn't strange,

16:32.280 --> 16:33.560
let alone a five-year gap.

16:34.200 --> 16:35.160
Besides,

16:35.240 --> 16:37.800
none of us thinks it's strange.

16:38.640 --> 16:40.000
Only you do.

16:40.080 --> 16:41.440
What are you so conflicted about?

16:50.080 --> 16:51.760
So what do you think I should do?

16:53.320 --> 16:54.200
First of all,

16:55.080 --> 16:56.480
stop thinking about the fact

16:56.560 --> 16:58.000
that he's older than you.

16:58.080 --> 16:59.640
Just interact with him

17:00.280 --> 17:01.520
naturally.

17:01.600 --> 17:02.480
Do you understand?

17:03.320 --> 17:04.599
Interact naturally.

17:06.280 --> 17:07.560
And secondly…

17:10.079 --> 17:11.880
If he doesn't make a move, I don't.

17:11.960 --> 17:13.920
But if he does, I strike first.

17:14.440 --> 17:15.359
Got it?

17:19.160 --> 17:20.160
Think about it carefully.

17:20.240 --> 17:21.520
I need to unpack my things.

17:25.079 --> 17:27.599
If he doesn't make a move, I don't.

17:29.080 --> 17:30.000
But if he does,

17:31.840 --> 17:32.920
I strike first.

17:42.440 --> 17:43.480
How did you meet him?

17:43.560 --> 17:45.160
We met while we hung out.

17:45.240 --> 17:46.440
Where?

17:46.520 --> 17:48.200
A bar.

17:50.520 --> 17:53.120
When you were drunk, you told me

17:53.200 --> 17:54.480
that you met him at a KTV.

17:57.240 --> 17:58.120
Yes.

17:59.080 --> 18:00.240
We met at a KTV.

18:01.680 --> 18:03.480
It looks like there is no such person.

18:04.960 --> 18:07.400
Could itreally be me?

18:09.840 --> 18:10.760
Hello, Shenlan.

18:12.200 --> 18:13.320
Call Qian Fei.

18:14.160 --> 18:16.560
QIAN FEI

18:16.640 --> 18:18.040
Hey, what's up?

18:18.120 --> 18:19.800
I'm busy right now. What is it?

18:19.880 --> 18:20.920
You're pretty smart.

18:21.640 --> 18:23.640
The guy that the girl said she likes

18:23.720 --> 18:24.880
is most likely me.

18:24.960 --> 18:26.240
Right? I was right!

18:26.320 --> 18:27.240
I knew it was you.

18:27.320 --> 18:29.120
I knew it the moment you described him.

18:29.960 --> 18:31.880
Since you're so clever, let me ask you.

18:32.480 --> 18:34.440
How did you win your wife's heart?

18:34.520 --> 18:36.680
Well, it's my charming personality.

18:37.760 --> 18:39.040
Why? Are you going to chase her?

18:39.120 --> 18:41.280
Just go ahead. She likes you, doesn't she?

18:41.360 --> 18:42.560
Just directly confess to her.

18:42.640 --> 18:44.640
No, I have to pursue her.

18:46.280 --> 18:47.640
Mainly, my girl

18:48.160 --> 18:49.360
has always felt

18:50.440 --> 18:51.800
that I couldn't possibly like her.

18:52.440 --> 18:54.440
So I have to be straightforward with her

18:54.520 --> 18:55.640
to make her happier.

18:55.720 --> 18:57.040
Your girl?

18:57.120 --> 18:58.560
How is she your girl now?

18:59.960 --> 19:00.800
Does she know

19:01.440 --> 19:03.720
that you already know she likes you?

19:05.080 --> 19:06.600
She doesn't know yet.

19:06.680 --> 19:08.840
So I have to pretend
that I don't know either.

19:09.360 --> 19:11.640
I have to save her face.

19:12.120 --> 19:14.200
As expected of you.

19:14.280 --> 19:15.800
When do you plan to tell her?

19:16.280 --> 19:17.880
Just tell me

19:17.960 --> 19:19.320
how you won over your wife.

19:20.160 --> 19:22.000
I'm busy right now, man.

19:22.080 --> 19:23.760
Stop bothering me. Let's talk later, okay?

19:24.520 --> 19:25.360
Don't forget.

19:25.440 --> 19:26.520
Okay, bye.

20:32.960 --> 20:34.520
DUAN JIAXU

20:34.600 --> 20:35.760
The woman

20:36.280 --> 20:38.200
that you saw at the airport before…

20:49.400 --> 20:50.800
JIAXU

20:54.360 --> 20:55.280
Sangsang!

20:55.360 --> 20:56.400
Keep it down.

20:57.240 --> 20:58.160
Sangsang!

20:58.720 --> 21:00.000
He is making his move!

21:00.680 --> 21:01.560
What?

21:02.200 --> 21:03.680
He is making his move.

21:03.760 --> 21:05.160
Should I make mine too?

21:05.240 --> 21:06.480
Yes.

21:06.560 --> 21:08.200
- Now? What do I do?
- Yes, now.

21:08.280 --> 21:09.640
Answer the call first.

21:09.720 --> 21:10.920
Answer it now.

21:11.000 --> 21:13.000
- I should head out.
- No, do it here. Right here.

21:13.080 --> 21:14.200
Answer it now.

21:14.280 --> 21:15.520
Hurry, or else, he will hang up.

21:16.280 --> 21:17.480
Hello?

21:20.960 --> 21:22.280
What took you so long to answer?

21:22.360 --> 21:23.200
Are you busy?

21:24.200 --> 21:25.080
No.

21:25.160 --> 21:26.080
What's going on?

21:26.600 --> 21:27.880
I'll tell you later.

21:31.000 --> 21:32.920
What day will you be free?

21:36.680 --> 21:38.120
Why? What is it?

21:39.000 --> 21:40.040
Nothing.

21:40.120 --> 21:41.600
I just want to take you out to a meal.

21:41.680 --> 21:42.680
A meal?

21:44.720 --> 21:45.720
He's asking her out.

21:46.840 --> 21:47.680
Can I?

21:49.240 --> 21:50.480
Sure.

21:52.720 --> 21:55.120
I still owe you a meal anyway.

21:56.920 --> 21:57.760
What do you mean?

21:58.320 --> 21:59.440
Are you saying

21:59.920 --> 22:01.760
that you will take this meal
I'll treat you to

22:01.840 --> 22:03.360
as the one you owed me last time?

22:03.440 --> 22:04.840
You'll get quite a good deal.

22:06.160 --> 22:08.000
So when are you free?

22:09.440 --> 22:10.960
Saturday. Wait, no.

22:11.040 --> 22:12.240
How about Friday?

22:12.760 --> 22:14.440
I have to go to the library to study

22:14.520 --> 22:16.160
with my classmates this Saturday.

22:16.240 --> 22:17.080
Okay.

22:17.840 --> 22:18.720
Then

22:19.360 --> 22:20.600
I'll send you the time

22:20.680 --> 22:22.520
and the name of the restaurant.

22:23.680 --> 22:24.520
Okay.

22:27.320 --> 22:28.440
That's all then.

22:28.520 --> 22:29.560
Bye.

22:32.040 --> 22:32.880
Bye.

22:46.280 --> 22:47.880
What's going on?

22:47.960 --> 22:49.120
Don't exclude the two of us.

22:49.760 --> 22:51.960
Sang Zhi's crush

22:52.040 --> 22:53.680
is asking her out!

22:53.760 --> 22:55.040
- Really?
- Crush?

22:55.600 --> 22:56.480
Do you mean the one

22:56.560 --> 22:57.960
whom you've had a secret crush on,

22:58.040 --> 22:59.400
works at a game studio,

22:59.480 --> 23:00.360
is very handsome,

23:00.440 --> 23:02.160
and you threw up on?

23:02.240 --> 23:04.400
Well, you don't have to mention

23:04.480 --> 23:05.520
that I threw up on him.

23:05.600 --> 23:06.600
Okay.

23:08.600 --> 23:09.800
So he asked you out for a meal.

23:11.440 --> 23:13.440
- That's great.
- It's working out, Sangsang.

23:13.520 --> 23:15.560
Your secret crush is about to turn real!

23:15.640 --> 23:16.720
What do you mean?

23:16.800 --> 23:17.960
It's not like we're strangers.

23:19.000 --> 23:20.640
What about you and Jiang Ming?

23:20.720 --> 23:21.800
You two--

23:21.880 --> 23:22.720
Me and him?

23:23.960 --> 23:26.600
We're just ordinary friends.

23:27.560 --> 23:28.840
I already made it clear to him.

23:32.120 --> 23:33.920
Sangsang sure is charming.

23:35.160 --> 23:36.400
He suddenly asked you out.

23:36.480 --> 23:37.840
Is he going to confess to you?

23:39.440 --> 23:40.760
Confess?

23:42.680 --> 23:44.080
That's not likely.

23:44.640 --> 23:47.280
We're just having a meal, I think.

23:47.360 --> 23:48.600
Why not?

23:48.680 --> 23:49.880
- I'm sure--
- Wait a minute.

23:51.040 --> 23:52.560
Since he has made his move,

23:52.640 --> 23:54.600
it's definitely more than just a meal.

23:55.240 --> 23:57.880
You have to be fully prepared.

23:57.960 --> 23:58.920
- She's right.
- Got it?

24:01.720 --> 24:03.280
Do something about your hair and outfit.

24:14.160 --> 24:16.000
MARCH 14TH, WEDNESDAY

24:16.080 --> 24:19.880
HE NEVER FORGOT
WHAT HE PROMISED ME BACK THEN

24:19.960 --> 24:21.760
I'M THE ONE WHO MISUNDERSTOOD HIM

24:24.840 --> 24:26.680
We did a couple of runs
with the QA engineer.

24:26.760 --> 24:28.960
The overall process
of the Celestial Progression System

24:29.040 --> 24:30.360
is already functional.

24:30.440 --> 24:32.000
The response capacity of the NPCs

24:32.080 --> 24:33.440
looks even more real than before.

24:34.360 --> 24:36.120
However, the AI's generalization ability

24:36.200 --> 24:37.440
is still not very strong.

24:38.440 --> 24:40.480
Dawang, do you have any ideas?

24:41.320 --> 24:44.080
Although we don't have beta testing yet,

24:44.160 --> 24:45.880
considering the level of completeness,

24:45.960 --> 24:48.280
I still have confidence
in the Celestial Progression System.

24:52.240 --> 24:53.200
What?

24:53.280 --> 24:55.640
I'm just stating
my opinion honestly, okay?

24:55.720 --> 24:56.760
Besides,

24:56.840 --> 24:58.200
there's still room for improvement.

24:58.280 --> 25:00.120
We just need to add more language data

25:00.200 --> 25:01.840
and expand our language database,

25:01.920 --> 25:03.200
so that players can feel

25:03.280 --> 25:05.840
that every character in our game world
truly exists.

25:07.200 --> 25:08.160
All right.

25:08.240 --> 25:10.360
Then we'll expand our learning library

25:10.440 --> 25:11.760
based on the players' profiles

25:11.840 --> 25:13.680
and their discussion points.

25:14.440 --> 25:15.400
Let's work hard

25:15.480 --> 25:17.520
to make the AI
more realistic and convincing.

25:18.480 --> 25:19.480
Next month,

25:19.560 --> 25:21.680
we'll invite players for a demo test.

25:22.240 --> 25:23.920
We're just a few months away from launch.

25:24.760 --> 25:26.520
Everyone, keep up the good work.

25:28.800 --> 25:30.480
Thank you, guys. I'll get going too.

25:30.560 --> 25:31.720
Thank you, Dawang. Bye.

25:36.080 --> 25:36.960
Jiaxu

25:37.520 --> 25:38.760
sure is a talented guy.

25:38.840 --> 25:40.640
He looks especially handsome today.

25:40.720 --> 25:41.560
What?

25:42.400 --> 25:44.280
You look cool today, Jiaxu.

25:59.840 --> 26:00.840
Work seriously.

26:06.880 --> 26:07.880
He's here.

26:09.120 --> 26:10.080
He's here.

26:10.160 --> 26:11.120
He's already here.

26:24.240 --> 26:25.400
Are you ready to go?

26:25.480 --> 26:26.680
I'll be right down.

26:30.400 --> 26:33.160
Sangsang, it's your first date.

26:34.480 --> 26:35.560
It's not a date.

26:36.200 --> 26:37.160
It's just a meal.

26:38.520 --> 26:39.720
- Right.
- Sure, it's a meal.

26:39.800 --> 26:40.880
You look pretty.

26:42.960 --> 26:44.080
If I go,

26:44.160 --> 26:46.120
will you guys feel lonely?

26:46.200 --> 26:48.040
Not at all. Just go.

26:49.440 --> 26:50.320
That's pretty.

26:50.400 --> 26:51.320
Bye.

26:51.400 --> 26:52.360
- Bye.
- Bye.

26:52.440 --> 26:53.600
- Be careful.
- Have a fun date.

26:56.600 --> 26:58.240
It feels like marrying off my daughter.

27:31.160 --> 27:32.120
What's wrong?

27:34.000 --> 27:35.080
You look pretty today.

27:42.080 --> 27:43.640
Later, we'll go to the restaurant

27:43.720 --> 27:44.760
we went to last time.

27:44.840 --> 27:46.600
I'll also introduce someone to you.

27:49.840 --> 27:51.040
Is someone else joining us?

27:51.120 --> 27:52.480
You'll find out later.

27:53.120 --> 27:54.000
Let's go.

27:57.840 --> 27:59.400
Didn't I promise you before?

28:00.080 --> 28:01.560
If I get a girlfriend,

28:02.080 --> 28:03.360
I'll introduce her to you first.

28:14.320 --> 28:16.320
If he has a girlfriend,

28:17.360 --> 28:19.680
I shouldn't sit
in the front passenger seat.

28:22.920 --> 28:24.400
Do you take me for a chauffeur?

28:44.560 --> 28:45.600
Buckle up.

29:04.040 --> 29:06.120
He seems to be in a good mood today.

29:07.800 --> 29:10.280
Is he really taking me
to meet his girlfriend?

29:21.560 --> 29:22.560
Over there.

29:28.680 --> 29:29.960
Let me make the introductions.

29:30.040 --> 29:31.280
This is Siyun,

29:32.000 --> 29:33.960
the producer of A Dream of Jianghu
and my superior.

29:34.720 --> 29:35.960
This is Sang Zhi.

29:38.080 --> 29:39.560
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

29:39.640 --> 29:41.400
Come and take a seat.

29:41.480 --> 29:42.680
Sit.

29:47.960 --> 29:49.240
I went with him

29:49.320 --> 29:50.760
to the airport to pick you up before.

29:50.840 --> 29:52.040
Do you still remember me?

29:52.720 --> 29:53.960
Yes, I do.

29:55.280 --> 29:58.560
I always hear Xiaoduan talk about you.

29:59.440 --> 30:01.640
I heard you're studying
at Yihe University.

30:03.680 --> 30:04.560
Yes.

30:04.640 --> 30:06.320
The last time I saw you,

30:06.400 --> 30:08.000
you were still in high school.

30:08.080 --> 30:09.400
Now you're so beautiful.

30:11.280 --> 30:12.800
You must be hungry. Here.

30:12.880 --> 30:14.680
Order what you want to eat.

30:16.240 --> 30:17.120
Go ahead.

30:20.800 --> 30:22.960
Siyun, have you ordered what you want?

30:23.040 --> 30:24.320
Yes, I've ordered some.

30:24.400 --> 30:25.880
See what you like to eat.

30:34.040 --> 30:34.960
Jiaxu.

30:36.120 --> 30:37.360
What do you want to eat?

30:38.760 --> 30:40.440
Why don't you and Siyun order first?

30:40.520 --> 30:41.520
I'm going to the restroom.

30:41.600 --> 30:42.440
Okay.

30:47.400 --> 30:48.560
Let's order these for now.

30:49.720 --> 30:50.920
Excuse me.

30:51.000 --> 30:51.920
Thank you.

30:56.800 --> 30:57.880
Last time,

30:57.960 --> 31:00.120
I didn't have a chance
to properly greet you

31:00.200 --> 31:02.360
when I met you at the airport.

31:03.080 --> 31:04.720
I'm sorry to have troubled you

31:05.400 --> 31:06.640
at the airport at that time.

31:06.720 --> 31:07.680
It was no trouble.

31:07.760 --> 31:10.760
I really shouldn't have tagged along.

31:11.720 --> 31:12.920
But I didn't think much of it.

31:13.000 --> 31:14.160
I just wanted to help.

31:15.320 --> 31:17.880
Xiaoduan had a mild fever that day.

31:18.560 --> 31:20.520
I wanted to have my husband drive him,

31:20.600 --> 31:22.640
but he had to meet a client
at the last minute,

31:22.720 --> 31:24.280
so I drove Jiaxu.

31:24.760 --> 31:26.560
He wasn't feeling well that day,

31:26.640 --> 31:29.480
so I got out of the car with him
to find you.

31:29.560 --> 31:31.600
Later, he even said

31:31.680 --> 31:33.400
he was afraid you might feel uncomfortable

31:33.480 --> 31:34.440
with a stranger around,

31:34.520 --> 31:35.760
so he asked me to leave first.

31:35.840 --> 31:37.480
That's why I left

31:37.560 --> 31:39.480
without telling you.

31:41.440 --> 31:43.040
No, it's okay.

31:43.120 --> 31:44.960
At first, I thought

31:45.040 --> 31:46.800
you were his relative's child

31:47.880 --> 31:49.800
because he was very angry that day.

31:49.880 --> 31:52.160
When you were crying in the restroom,

31:52.240 --> 31:53.880
he was still talking about it.

31:53.960 --> 31:55.280
The restroom is over there.

31:56.920 --> 31:57.800
Go now.

31:57.880 --> 31:59.080
We'll have a nice lunch later.

32:05.680 --> 32:06.560
It's all right.

32:07.520 --> 32:08.640
I remember

32:08.720 --> 32:10.240
when I first met her.

32:10.800 --> 32:12.360
She was wrestling with her brother

32:12.440 --> 32:13.480
and could cry on a dime.

32:15.120 --> 32:16.680
Her biggest worry in the past

32:16.760 --> 32:18.480
was probably
getting into trouble at school.

32:21.280 --> 32:22.320
But just now,

32:24.000 --> 32:26.160
when I saw her holding back tears,

32:29.080 --> 32:30.160
my heart broke for her.

32:31.120 --> 32:32.600
That's how young girls are.

32:32.680 --> 32:34.280
They'll grow up eventually.

32:34.840 --> 32:35.920
Don't be too worried.

32:40.960 --> 32:41.800
So

32:42.520 --> 32:44.480
that was what they were talking about.

32:46.120 --> 32:47.960
I actually thought they were…

32:48.440 --> 32:49.840
What's wrong?

32:51.120 --> 32:52.000
It's nothing.

32:57.680 --> 32:58.680
Xiaoduan

32:59.520 --> 33:00.760
is a great guy.

33:02.160 --> 33:03.640
He's young and promising.

33:03.720 --> 33:04.720
He's also good-looking.

33:04.800 --> 33:06.080
The most important thing is that

33:06.160 --> 33:07.720
since I've known him,

33:07.800 --> 33:08.880
he has been single

33:09.560 --> 33:12.000
and hasn't been involved
in any messy relationship.

33:12.520 --> 33:14.120
To be honest,

33:14.200 --> 33:15.760
I'm really curious

33:15.840 --> 33:18.320
what kind of woman he will end up with.

33:20.040 --> 33:21.480
Here, have some more water.

33:22.360 --> 33:23.320
Thank you.

33:28.160 --> 33:29.320
What are you guys doing here?

33:30.680 --> 33:33.080
We were going to have a team meal today.

33:33.160 --> 33:34.960
This restaurant came up with good reviews,

33:35.040 --> 33:36.360
so I brought everyone here.

33:38.520 --> 33:40.880
Jiaxu, who is this?

33:43.760 --> 33:44.880
- Who is she?
- Who is she?

33:45.360 --> 33:46.440
Introduce her to us.

33:47.200 --> 33:48.080
A friend.

33:48.920 --> 33:49.920
A friend?

33:50.000 --> 33:51.640
- What kind of friend?
- Tell us.

33:52.520 --> 33:54.080
He said friend,

33:54.840 --> 33:55.960
not sister.

33:56.720 --> 33:58.880
In the past,
he always called me his sister

33:58.960 --> 34:00.440
or a relative's child.

34:01.560 --> 34:03.120
Xiaoduan, make the introduction.

34:03.200 --> 34:04.080
Come on.

34:04.640 --> 34:06.200
My friend's name is Sang Zhi.

34:06.280 --> 34:07.880
She's studying at a university here.

34:08.960 --> 34:10.040
This is Li Xun,

34:10.120 --> 34:12.400
our company's middleware consultant

34:12.480 --> 34:13.960
and Siyun's husband.

34:14.040 --> 34:14.880
I'm Li Xun.

34:14.960 --> 34:16.120
Hello, Li Xun.

34:16.199 --> 34:17.920
Hi, I'm Jia Yang,

34:18.000 --> 34:19.199
Jiaxu's junior.

34:19.280 --> 34:21.000
- Hello.
- Hi, you can call me Xiaobai.

34:21.560 --> 34:22.679
Hello, I'm Zhang Sen.

34:22.760 --> 34:23.880
I'm also Jiaxu's junior.

34:23.960 --> 34:25.280
Hello, I'm Xiaobo.

34:25.360 --> 34:26.600
- Hello.
- Hi, I'm Xiaomi.

34:26.679 --> 34:27.600
- Hello.
- Hi.

34:27.679 --> 34:28.840
Nice to meet you.

34:29.440 --> 34:31.480
I thought you were here to eat. Go on.

34:31.560 --> 34:32.840
Wait. Why don't we eat together?

34:32.920 --> 34:34.000
It's a company gathering.

34:34.080 --> 34:35.760
Since you're his friend, join us.

34:35.840 --> 34:36.760
Excuse me.

34:36.840 --> 34:39.239
- Can we join the tables?
- Come and help out.

34:39.320 --> 34:40.360
Let's join the tables.

34:40.440 --> 34:41.440
I'll help you.

34:42.080 --> 34:43.000
Menu, please.

34:50.159 --> 34:51.600
How about we eat elsewhere?

34:52.400 --> 34:53.280
Can we?

34:53.840 --> 34:56.120
Li Xun, Siyun, we have plans.

34:56.199 --> 34:57.560
Enjoy. We'll leave first.

34:57.640 --> 34:58.600
Are you not joining us?

34:58.680 --> 34:59.880
You guys can go ahead.

34:59.960 --> 35:01.400
Bye, Siyun. Bye, Li Xun.

35:01.480 --> 35:03.200
- Are you leaving?
- Why aren't you joining us?

35:03.280 --> 35:05.360
- Jiaxu, why are you leaving?
- Why did he leave?

35:12.160 --> 35:13.200
What do you want to eat?

35:13.280 --> 35:14.360
I'll make a reservation.

35:26.120 --> 35:28.120
I'm not hungry yet.

35:29.040 --> 35:30.040
Jiaxu.

35:30.120 --> 35:32.760
Let's not come to this restaurant again.

35:32.840 --> 35:35.120
I feel that we're not meant to eat here.

35:37.400 --> 35:39.720
They just wanted to join in the fun.

35:39.800 --> 35:40.760
They meant no harm.

35:40.840 --> 35:41.920
I know.

35:42.000 --> 35:43.520
I meant this restaurant.

35:46.440 --> 35:47.360
All right.

35:48.760 --> 35:51.000
Let's find somewhere else to eat.

35:54.040 --> 35:54.920
Jiaxu.

35:56.240 --> 35:58.360
Did you ask Siyun to explain it to me?

36:03.520 --> 36:04.600
Did she tell you?

36:08.840 --> 36:10.240
Yes, she told me.

36:11.320 --> 36:12.160
Jiaxu.

36:13.280 --> 36:14.360
Didn't you tell me

36:14.440 --> 36:15.720
at the airport at the time?

36:16.560 --> 36:17.640
I believed you.

36:18.920 --> 36:19.760
Is that so?

36:26.200 --> 36:27.440
I know

36:27.520 --> 36:28.800
girls your age

36:29.400 --> 36:33.040
always like to believe
in some strange sixth sense.

36:34.560 --> 36:36.280
And I don't want you to misunderstand.

36:36.360 --> 36:37.200
Or else…

36:39.520 --> 36:40.680
It will be troublesome later.

36:55.840 --> 36:57.480
So where are we going later?

37:00.160 --> 37:01.200
Well,

37:02.040 --> 37:03.080
if you don't want to eat,

37:03.160 --> 37:04.240
why don't we watch a movie?

37:05.240 --> 37:07.560
The theatrical version of an anime
came out recently.

37:09.400 --> 37:11.520
I happen to know a theater nearby.

37:24.640 --> 37:25.560
It should be ahead.

37:26.160 --> 37:27.200
We still have 15 minutes.

37:27.280 --> 37:28.320
We can take our time.

37:32.560 --> 37:35.440
Jiaxu, can I order a drink?

37:35.960 --> 37:37.880
Sure. What do you want?

37:41.240 --> 37:43.600
- I'll have white peach oolong tea.
- Welcome.

37:43.680 --> 37:44.680
I want 30% sugar.

37:44.760 --> 37:46.400
White peach oolong with 30% sugar.

37:46.960 --> 37:48.360
Large and make it hot.

37:48.440 --> 37:49.320
YU XIN

37:49.400 --> 37:50.840
- How are things?
- Anything else?

37:50.920 --> 37:52.520
No, thank you.

37:52.600 --> 37:53.760
Just one cup?

37:55.160 --> 37:56.120
Yes. How much is it?

37:56.200 --> 37:57.120
Scan the code here.

37:57.960 --> 38:00.080
One hot white peach oolong with 30% sugar.

38:00.160 --> 38:01.040
It's done.

38:01.120 --> 38:02.720
I might

38:02.800 --> 38:04.320
be back late.

38:05.200 --> 38:08.640
- She's coming back late.
- Late? What time exactly?

38:08.720 --> 38:09.800
What's the situation?

38:09.880 --> 38:10.920
Let's ask her.

38:11.480 --> 38:12.800
Then

38:12.880 --> 38:14.640
does that mean it's a success?

38:15.720 --> 38:17.960
- Don't come back.
- Seriously?

38:18.040 --> 38:19.240
Something is up!

38:19.320 --> 38:21.360
Was I right? Did he confess?

38:21.440 --> 38:22.480
No.

38:22.560 --> 38:24.280
We're going to watch a movie.

38:24.360 --> 38:26.080
Is it the theatrical version of the anime?

38:26.160 --> 38:28.480
- Didn't we agree to watch it together?
- Who are you texting?

38:31.640 --> 38:32.520
My roommates.

38:33.880 --> 38:35.880
Hi, your white peach oolong is ready.

38:35.960 --> 38:37.960
Is it for drinking now or takeaway?

38:38.040 --> 38:39.000
- Now.
- Drinking now.

38:41.760 --> 38:42.960
Here.

38:43.840 --> 38:44.720
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

38:44.800 --> 38:46.520
- Have a good day.
- Can you throw this for me?

38:46.600 --> 38:47.520
Sure.

38:48.280 --> 38:49.240
Don't you want a drink?

38:49.760 --> 38:50.960
I'll buy a bottle of water

38:51.040 --> 38:52.040
at the theater later.

38:55.040 --> 38:56.200
What's so funny?

38:56.280 --> 38:57.320
As expected of you.

38:58.360 --> 38:59.200
What about me?

39:00.400 --> 39:01.840
Nothing much. It's just very healthy.

39:03.400 --> 39:04.440
Healthy?

39:07.200 --> 39:08.120
What's wrong?

39:09.840 --> 39:10.960
Why is it milk tea?

39:11.520 --> 39:12.400
Milk tea?

39:14.520 --> 39:15.720
It really is milk tea.

39:16.360 --> 39:17.840
Did they get the cups mixed up?

39:19.920 --> 39:21.760
Don't tell me you're allergic to milk tea.

39:23.800 --> 39:24.760
I'm allergic to milk.

39:26.160 --> 39:28.400
But it's okay. I only took a small sip.

39:29.280 --> 39:30.800
Do you feel any discomfort?

39:30.880 --> 39:31.960
No.

39:34.880 --> 39:36.040
Wait here for me.

39:36.120 --> 39:37.200
I'll get you another drink.

39:37.800 --> 39:39.160
Are you really okay?

39:48.520 --> 39:49.880
I bought you tea.

39:49.960 --> 39:50.960
Okay. Thank you.

39:51.040 --> 39:52.680
What happened to your face?

39:53.840 --> 39:55.240
A rash is breaking out.

39:55.320 --> 39:56.680
Don't touch it with your hand.

39:59.960 --> 40:01.160
I'll take you to the hospital.

40:01.240 --> 40:02.560
No, I'll just buy some medicine.

40:03.120 --> 40:04.000
Listen to me.

40:04.840 --> 40:06.000
- Let's go.
- Wait.

40:06.520 --> 40:07.880
What about the movie?

40:08.440 --> 40:09.440
We'll watch it next time.

40:15.600 --> 40:17.440
Why did it have to be today?

40:19.640 --> 40:21.680
- Thank you.
- We couldn't even watch the movie.

40:22.840 --> 40:24.120
How frustrating.

40:28.320 --> 40:30.040
Here. Take the medicine.

40:35.440 --> 40:37.280
It should make you feel better.

40:40.320 --> 40:41.640
The doctor said to take two pills.

41:27.960 --> 41:29.120
Siyun.

41:30.240 --> 41:31.120
What a coincidence.

41:31.200 --> 41:32.160
How so?

41:34.400 --> 41:36.800
I happened to see a cake on my way in,

41:36.880 --> 41:38.120
so I bought it for you.

41:39.160 --> 41:40.720
What do you want?

41:43.080 --> 41:44.040
Siyun.

41:44.800 --> 41:46.040
Are you free this Friday?

41:46.120 --> 41:47.680
I want to buy you a meal

41:47.760 --> 41:50.040
and ask you for a favor.

41:51.240 --> 41:52.240
What kind of favor?

41:53.880 --> 41:55.600
Well, do you remember

41:55.680 --> 41:57.280
the girl that you went with me to pick up

41:57.360 --> 41:58.320
at the airport before?

42:00.040 --> 42:01.400
Your relative's kid.

42:02.360 --> 42:03.520
She might have misunderstood

42:04.400 --> 42:06.800
that you're my girlfriend.

42:06.880 --> 42:08.480
I want you to help me explain it to her.

42:08.560 --> 42:10.240
Sure, no problem.

42:10.760 --> 42:12.120
I'll find an opportunity

42:12.200 --> 42:14.360
to talk to her over the meal.

42:17.080 --> 42:18.040
By the way,

42:18.120 --> 42:19.800
can you also tell her

42:19.880 --> 42:23.040
that I haven't had a girlfriend for years?

42:24.720 --> 42:25.880
Do I have to mention that too?

42:26.800 --> 42:27.680
Okay.

42:28.200 --> 42:29.760
Is there anything else?

42:29.840 --> 42:30.800
That's all.

42:31.800 --> 42:33.040
Can I leave after the meal?

42:34.160 --> 42:35.160
Okay.

42:35.240 --> 42:36.280
I won't be the third wheel.

42:38.720 --> 42:40.640
- I'll get back to work.
- Go on.

42:40.720 --> 42:41.920
Thank you, Siyun.

42:47.920 --> 42:49.080
One more thing.

42:49.160 --> 42:50.720
What else do you want me to tell her?

42:51.560 --> 42:54.120
When you say that I haven't been dating,

42:54.200 --> 42:55.440
can you make it sound natural?

42:55.520 --> 42:57.480
- It's just--
- Okay.

42:57.560 --> 42:58.680
I don't need you to teach me.

42:59.280 --> 43:00.480
Duan Jiaxu.

43:00.560 --> 43:03.360
Why are you acting
like an inexperienced young boy?
